    <p><strong>Video Reserves:</strong> Your instructor will add a tool to your Sakai course called <strong>Video Reserves</strong>. This tool will provide seamless access to all of the digitized videos your professor has requested for your course. You will able to stream the videos from directly in Sakai.</p>
    <p><strong>All other reserves:</strong> Your instructor will be given instructions on adding a generic web tool which will link directly into the remainder of your course reserves. This will include all reserves except streaming video.</p>
    <p><strong>Questions?</strong> Please contact the library or the OIT Help Desk (<a href="mailto:oithelp@nd.edu">oithelp@nd.edu</a>) if you have any questions about reserves or how to access them within Sakai.</p>
